{"tid":1548023,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"抵制黨鐵 唔好再用八達通","createTime":"2019-09-07T01:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T03:48:01.000Z","uid":14699,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"73841aed824708a0486a7f4301b9d313cfa9fb76","tid":1548023,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:35:03.000Z","msg":"抵制黨鐵好多種方法<br />\n除左唔搭黨鐵/跳閘<br />\n唔去黨鐵商場消費<br />\n仲有最低成本既停用八達通<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搭車買野都唔好再用八達通</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vr4tLQx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvr4tLQx.jpg&h=5a7591d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">公司於2019年首六個月應佔八達通控股有限公司的利潤上升22.4%至1.20億港元，主要由於交易量及八達通產品銷售收入均有所上升。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/archive/corporate/ch/investor/interim2019/CMTRIR19.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Farchive%2Fcorporate%2Fch%2Finvestor%2Finterim2019%2FCMTRIR19.pdf&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=82bc03a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/archive/corporate/ch/investor/interim2019/CMTRIR19.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n跳閘你就話唔敢姐<br />\n唔係唔用張八達通都做唔到呀<br />\n<br />\n巴士就入返銀<br />\nOK 7仔 出街食飯買野用現金/Apple Pay/Google Pay/Samsung Pay<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵而家出賣緊香港人既人生安全</span><br />\n咪同我講唔方便乜乜乜"},{"pid":"79b701acd1764ee58580e6115659a1c1102d50bd","tid":1548023,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:36:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d34f6be8e6287db3dc5a348fdaa773b6ba787836","tid":1548023,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:37:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fbf22a7ac419fc59163583c9bab1fb93f40c4da","tid":1548023,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:38:12.000Z","msg":"買嘢有得用信用卡一定用Apple Pay找數<br />\n坐車就用綠卡<br />\n係有啲地方只限八達通先會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416ce8a4da312419df7c183a69e39cade56fd5c1","tid":1548023,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:41:28.000Z","msg":"同埋咪再送data比黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdf65bc3323df80deff856a65e33a4f1b53426a","tid":1548023,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fdd0df44cc0dce4e1bcd16201ea83fee908bd820","tid":1548023,"uid":53803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"不如約齊人一齊去某個站退八達通錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每人100蚊<br />\n黨鐵未必準備到咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d236d204c644f3883737240ee2a966bb73b93c9f","tid":1548023,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdd0df44cc0dce4e1bcd16201ea83fee908bd820","tid":1548023,"uid":53803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"不如約齊人一齊去某個站退八達通錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每人100蚊<br />\n黨鐵未必準備到咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:46:04.000Z","msg":"有得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b12827fd1de119772a3fc867305660e389194e","tid":1548023,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:54:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a549815c7095950148303e4903848298b260793c","tid":1548023,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4f6469f5f1aabdb7e1